{"tid":1850300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"低風險人士用自己的烤箱自行消毒口罩重用，可行嗎？","createTime":"2020-01-29T12:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T13:14:04.000Z","uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb98bd7abd3653793062b2e93032f16d325a4d3","tid":1850300,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"想請教下各專家的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/7/1/26/n1603781.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F7%2F1%2F26%2Fn1603781.htm&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=102969f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/7/1/26/n1603781.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者汪淑芬台北二十六日電）三年多前SARS(嚴重急性呼吸道症候群)流行期間，N95口罩成為搶手貨，一度不敷使用，為因應未來可能發生防疫物資不足的情況，行政院勞委會勞工安全衛生研究所研究發現，<span style=\"color: blue;\">乾熱及紫外線是對口罩過濾影響最小的滅菌方式</span>⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n勞研所日前完成包括疾病管制局、各縣市衛生局及大型醫院庫存N95口罩的滅菌及儲放影響研究，以大腸桿菌模擬病毒噴布於市售六款N95口罩上，經測試乾熱（烘箱）、濕熱（蒸鍋）、高溫高壓滅菌、紫外光及噴灑酒精五種滅菌方法，再利用拋棄式防塵口罩的國家標準，觀察重複使用可行性。<br />\n<br />\n研究結果顯示，五種滅菌方式在一定條件下都能完殺死口罩上的大腸桿菌，其中<span style=\"color: blue;\">以攝氏七十度的烘箱作用三十分鐘的乾熱法，與作用三十秒紫外線滅菌法，對口罩的過濾效果影響最小，六款測試口罩的過濾效果，都還可維持在百分之九十五以上。</span>"},{"pid":"ab66c09e8d15502747235f3ce855bfbda162f12a","tid":1850300,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68d031ed5e72b094cd8f97b1084e331f9df3187","tid":1850300,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:03:58.000Z","msg":"[行動]連儂/文宣十八區開花! A4 label周圍貼! 大量現成圖-即print 即貼(3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13fa7bf8eaa4f59de4682ab0f6c24e05d3bd0509","tid":1850300,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"而家係病毒喎<br />\n殺得死病菌＝殺得死病毒？<br />\n<br />\n申請唔識，等解答"},{"pid":"34c39ff5251ddeb68e2e2f25ee475e1cf7fc47f4","tid":1850300,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13fa7bf8eaa4f59de4682ab0f6c24e05d3bd0509","tid":1850300,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"而家係病毒喎<br />\n殺得死病菌＝殺得死病毒？<br />\n<br />\n申請唔識，等解答"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:14:04.000Z","msg":"利申*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}